_:N2ffb485cdb8449e3acd324baa8979975 <http://schema.org/headLine> "Personal information charter" .
_:N2ffb485cdb8449e3acd324baa8979975 <http://schema.org/image> <https://www.gov.uk/assets/frontend/govuk_publishing_components/govuk-schema-placeholder-1x1-2672c0fb7a5d5f947d880522c509ebe7f2be090885883cc94418f6860e812e15.png> .
